AD_TABLE.NAME: Obpos_CChannel_SelWarehouse
AD_TABLE.HQLQUERY: select e.id as id, e.organization as organization, e.name as name, e.searchKey as searchKey, locationAddress, e.allocated as allocated, (select (case when count(*) = 0 then false else true end) from OBPOS_OrgWarehouseExtra as ow where ow.organization.id = :OBPOS_replace_org_id and ow.warehouseType = :warehouseType and ow.warehouse.id= e.id) as OB_Selected, locationAddress.postalCode as postalCode, region, country from Warehouse as e left join e.locationAddress as locationAddress left join locationAddress.country as country left join locationAddress.region as region where @additional_filters@
